com.baypackets.ase.sbb
Interface MessageFilter

public interface MessageFilter

The MessageFilter interface provides a callback to an SBB object so that it can perform various manipulations to SIP messages before the SBB sends them to the network. Modifications performed by this object must conform to JSR 116; this includes SDP and/or non-system header changes.

Author:
BayPackets
